#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Company specific offers</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Penawaran khusus perusahaan</strong>"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Do you want to go further?</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Apakah Anda ingin melanjutkan?</strong>"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Final word</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Kata-kata terakhir</strong>"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>In such situation, feel free to experiment with this database and "
"then to create a new one for your own usage.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Di situasi seperti ini, jangan ragu untuk bereksperimen dengan "
"database ini dan lalu membuat database baru untuk Anda gunakan.</strong>"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Multiple resource blocking / period closure</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Blocking beberapa sumber daya / penutupan periode</strong>"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Shared offers</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Penawaran bersama</strong>"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Single resource blocking</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Blocking sumber daya tunggal</strong>"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Use case</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Kasus penggunaan</strong>"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model:product.template,name:holiday_house.product_template_13
msgid "A-frame Cabin"
msgstr "Cabin A-Frame"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Access the rates from the same menu to see how price rules apply during the "
"year."
msgstr ""
"Akses tarif dari menu yang sama untuk melihat penerapan peraturan harga "
"sepanjang tahun."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Access to more details clicking the slot."
msgstr "Klik slot ini untuk melihat detail lengkapnya."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.homepage
msgid ""
"Accommodation were exactly what we needed for a family moment.<br/>Many "
"thanks agan."
msgstr ""
"Akomodasi ini persis seperti yang kami butuhkan untuk momen keluarga.<br/"
">Terima kasih banyak."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Add here as many of them as needed."
msgstr "Tambahkan di sini sebanyak mungkin yang dibutuhkan."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Adjust the number of stars, leave a comment and send it!"
msgstr "Sesuaikan jumlah bintang, beri komentar, lalu kirimkan!"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Adjust the rental dates, click the book button and then proceed to checkout."
msgstr ""
"Sesuaikan tanggal rental, klik tombol \"pesan\", lalu lanjutkan ke checkout."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Adjust your prices along the year"
msgstr "Menyesuaikan harga seiring berjalannya tahun"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Adjusting your offers in consequence"
msgstr "Menyesuaikan penawaran secara berkala"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Again, the <strong>Holiday House App </strong>helps you manage the end of "
"the stay!"
msgstr ""
"Sekali lagi, aplikasi <strong>Rumah Rumah Liburan </strong>membantu Anda "
"mengelola akhir masa inap!"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.custom_product_name
msgid "All Houses"
msgstr "Semua Rumah"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternatively to individual resource blocking slots described earlier, you "
"can select a resource this leave applies to."
msgstr ""
"Selain slot blocking sumber daya satuan yang dijelaskan sebelumnya, Anda "
"dapat memilih sumber daya yang berlaku untuk cuti ini."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternatively, switch to the list view, which is more suitable if the "
"booking is not during the visualized date range and update the booking date "
"range."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga bisa beralih ke tampilan daftar, yang lebih cocok jika pemesanan "
"tidak dalam rentang tanggal yang ditampilkan, dan memperbarui rentang "
"tanggal pemesanan."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternatively, type in the search bar and select the appropriate filter."
msgstr "Atau, ketik di kolom pencarian dan pilih filter yang sesuai."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can create a slot as placeholder from the planning "
"directly:"
msgstr ""
"Anda juga dapat membuat slot sebagai placeholder langsung dari perencanaan:"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.homepage
msgid ""
"Amazing stay at the heart of a pine tree forest. Resourcing and peaceful. "
"<br/>Lovely furnished with all the necessary, even including games such as "
"Mölkky. <br/>I can only recommend!"
msgstr ""
"Pengalaman menginap yang berkesan di tengah hutan pinus. Menenangkan dan "
"damai. <br/>Dilengkapi perabotan yang indah lengkap, bahkan ada permainan "
"seperti Mölkky. <br/>Saya sangat merekomendasikannya!"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:product.template,website_description:holiday_house.product_template_12
#: model_terms:product.template,website_description:holiday_house.product_template_13
#: model_terms:product.template,website_description:holiday_house.product_template_14
msgid "An address must be specified for a map to be embedded"
msgstr "Alamat yang harus ditetapkan untuk peta yang akan di embed"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "An automation is setup for an email to be sent automatically for you."
msgstr ""
"Sistem otomatisasi telah disiapkan agar email dikirimkan secara otomatis "
"untuk Anda."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Any time you create a new survey and save it with the setting \"is customer "
"satisfaction survey\", previous ones\n"
"                will be archived so that it becomes your new default survey."
msgstr ""
"Setiap kali Anda membuat survei baru dan menyimpannya dengan pengaturan "
"\"adalah survei kepuasan pelanggan\",\n"
"                survei sebelumnya akan diarsipkan sehingga menjadi survei "
"default yang baru."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Anyone can create a portal account on your database.<br/>\n"
"Open your website home page in a private tab to do so."
msgstr ""
"Siapa pun dapat membuat akun portal di database Anda.<br/>\n"
"Buka halaman beranda website di tab pribadi untuk melakukannya."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Assign them a resource, which helps you keeping track."
msgstr "Tetapkan sumber daya kepadanya untuk membantu pelacakan."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"At any time from the guest order, use the Send message capability in the "
"chatter to exchange with your guest."
msgstr ""
"Kapan pun dari pesanan tamu, gunakan fitur Kirim pesan di Chatter untuk "
"berkomunikasi dengan tamu Anda."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"At any time you can adjust the city tax count delivered by re-opening the "
"city tax widget clicking the City Tax button on the guest order."
msgstr ""
"Jumlah pajak kota yang ditampilkan dapat disesuaikan kapan saja dengan "
"membuka kembali widget pajak kota, mengeklik tombol Pajak Kota pada pesanan "
"tamu."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model:product.template,name:holiday_house.product_template_14
msgid "Beach House"
msgstr "Rumah Pantai"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Because keeping an eye on your business performance matter, the module comes "
"with a dedicated dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Mengingat pentingnya pemantauan performa bisnis Anda, modul ini dilengkapi "
"dengan dashboard khusus."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Beyond daily operations, the Steering menu serves as the \"Captain’s "
"Bridge\" of your holiday houses. It provides a 500-day horizon to anticipate "
"market trends, manage risks, and optimize your revenue."
msgstr ""
"Selain untuk operasi harian, menu Steering berfungsi sebagai \"Pusat "
"Kendali\" rumah liburan Anda. Fitur ini memberikan insight 500 hari ke depan "
"untuk mengantisipasi tren pasar, mengelola risiko, dan mengoptimalkan "
"pendapatan Anda."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Blocking resources"
msgstr "Blocking sumber daya"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Booking a house"
msgstr "Memesan rumah"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"By uploading this module's demo data, your database has been filled with a "
"few products, sale orders and more."
msgstr ""
"Dengan mengunggah data demo modul ini, database Anda telah diisi dengan "
"beberapa produk, pesanan penjualan, dan lebih banyak lagi."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Charge your customer for the resulting amount and you're all set!"
msgstr "Tagih pelanggan Anda sesuai jumlah akhir dan semuanya beres!"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Charge your guests"
msgstr "Membuat tagihan untuk tamu"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Check and adjust if needed the number of guest who stayed in each room. Then "
"confirm the number of city tax to be charged, which updated the delivered "
"city tax count."
msgstr ""
"Periksa dan sesuaikan (bila perlu) jumlah tamu yang menginap di setiap "
"kamar. Setelah itu, konfirmasi jumlah pajak kota yang akan dikenakan. "
"Nantinya, jumlah pajak kota yang telah disampaikan akan diperbarui."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Check guests in"
msgstr "Melakukan check-in tamu"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Check guests out"
msgstr "Melakukan check-out tamu"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Check the invoice data and confirm it."
msgstr "Periksa data faktur, lalu konfirmasi."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"City Taxes are to be billed to spent nights in practice and not in theory "
"and are counted as the sum of nights each guest stayed."
msgstr ""
"Pajak Kota harus ditagih berdasarkan jumlah malam aktual yang dihabiskan, "
"bukan secara teoritis, dan dihitung sebagai jumlah total malam yang "
"dihabiskan oleh setiap tamu."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Click one of the house to book."
msgstr "Klik salah satu rumah untuk dipesan."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Click the Check in button to confirm they are now staying at your place!"
msgstr ""
"Klik tombol Check in untuk mengonfirmasi bahwa tamu kini menginap di tempat "
"Anda!"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Click the Check out button to capture they return you the keys."
msgstr "Klik tombol Check out untuk merekam pengembalian kunci."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Click the Create Order to open the order form."
msgstr "Klik Buat Pesanan untuk membuka formulir pesanan."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Click the Invoice button with a full invoice."
msgstr "Klik tombol Faktur dengan faktur lengkap."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Click the Pay with demo button, and then Pay button to mimic the payment."
msgstr ""
"Klik tombol Bayar dengan demo, lalu tombol Bayar untuk menguji coba "
"pembayaran."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Click the tail of the corresponding booking and drag it to the requested "
"date."
msgstr ""
